OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FGermany beer bottle        
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fshortage: Industry warns of
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F'tense' situation          
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, German breweries are warning there     
OL,6, could be a shortage of beer bottles    
OL,7, this summer amid rising production     
OL,8, costs and a shortage of lorry drivers. 
OL,10,FThe situation is "extremely tense", the
OL,11,Fchief executive of the German Brewers' 
OL,12,FFederation told German newspaper Bild. 
OL,14,FThe shortage of glass bottles will     
OL,15,Fmainly affect small- and medium-sized  
OL,16,Fbreweries, an industry expert said.    
OL,18,FBrewers are having to pay 80% more for 
OL,19,Fnew glass bottles than they did a year 
OL,20,Fago. The cost of beer is also rising.  
